        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Do SEO content writing software platforms actually help rankings?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes, when used correctly. The NLP scoring layer (Surfer, NeuronWriter) closes intent gaps in your drafts. The generation layer (Jasper, theStacc) speeds publishing cadence. The combination of cadence + on-page coverage is what moves the needle, not either alone." }},
